title: Last Life - Season 1 S01 Complete WebRip.x264-SBC
description:
Last Life is a fantasy, drama about reincarnation, soul mates and the ancient battle between good and evil. Sloane, with whom Taylor has shared many lifetimes, sets out to rescue her soul mate from the snares of light-witch coven, The Alina. Sloane tries to help Taylor remember who she is, before dark-witch coven, The Blood Born, can use her to fulfill a dark destiny.
